quote: You may find your exasperation turns to inspiration
I saw a friend of mine who had suffered a very heavy contusion after an accident
I don't know how to adjust my life . Would you give me a piece of advice ?
That's too bad.What kind of accident is it ? Are you all right ?
Sometimes life hits you in the head with a brick. Don't lose faith.
I had an accident with damage to the car body.
When I broke my leg I felt fear.
Inspiration exists, but it has to find us working.
